body: There is currently a command line version of TOCO that supports SavedModels ([example](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/master/tensorflow/contrib/lite/toco/g3doc/cmdline_examples.md)). There is some work being done to improve this tooling including adding a Python API for SavedModels (which should be available externally by end of this week). The [documentation](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/tree/master/tensorflow/contrib/lite/toco) will be updated as these changes are made.
